lead_paragraph: Villanova starts its fourth week as the No. 1 team in The Associated Press Top 25 and the ranked teams stay the same from the last poll except for Florida, which replaces fellow Southeastern Conference member South Carolina.

headline.print_headline: Villanova on Top of AP Poll for Fourth Straight Week
